{"cell_id": "r1c1", "row": 1, "col": 1, "text": "PLOGI and FLOGI\nPLOGI FLOGI LS_ACC\nLS_ACC Parameter Parameter\nParameter applicability applicability\napplicability\nDefault Class Class Class\nLogin\nService Parameter Word Bits Value 1a 2 3 1a 2 3 1a 2 3\nBB_SC_N 1 15-12 0 y y y y y y y y y\nBuffer-to-Buffer Receive Data Field 1 11-0 128 y y y y y y y y y\nSize\nNx_Port Total Concurrent 2 31-16 1 y y y n n n n n n\nSequences\nRelative offset by Info Category 2 15-0 0 y y y n n n n n n\nR_A_TOV 2 31-0 10 000 n n n n n n y y y\nE_D_TOV Value 3 31-0 2 000 yb yb yb n n n y y y\nLegend:\n\"y\" indicates yes, applicable (i.e., has meaning);\n\"n\" indicates no, not applicable (i.e., has no meaning)\na The Class 1 Service Parameters shall be used for Class 6. Each has the same applicability as Class 1.\nb E_D_TOV resolution and the corresponding value are only meaningful in a point-to-point topology or when\ndoing PLOGI with an NL_Port on the same loop.\nc The Common Service Parameter applicability is specified in FC-SP.\nd Default buffer-to-buffer credit = 1 for all ports but an L_Port, and Buffer-to-buffer credit=0 for an L_Port.\ne N_Port/F_Port=0 for an N_Port, and N_Port/F_Port=1 for an F_Port.\nf BB_Credit Management=0 for an N_Port or F_Port, BB_Credit_Management=1 for an L_Port", "page": 169, "bbox": [94.61, 76.87, 539.52, 503.4]}
